Package: focus-stack
Architecture: any
Depends: libopencv-dev, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgcc1, libstdc++6
Suggests: ocl-icd-libopencl1
Description: Fast focus stacking of photos for extended depth of field.
 focus-stack implements the complex wavelets based algorithm for
 combining multiple photos with different focus level to one
 extended depth of field photo.
